iption_plain":"Struggling to find a link that lobsters allows. But unions have been merged into dotnet 11:\r\n\r\nJulien Couvreur (@jcouv)\r\nWe merged an early C# 15 preview feature into .NET 11 preview 3: unions.\r\n\r\nAdds union declarations (`union Pet(Cat, Dog, Bird) { ... }`) and union types (attributed with `[Union]`).\r\nThey can be treated by pattern matching/switch expressions as a closed set for exhaustiveness.","submitter_user":"martinald","user_is_author":false,"tags":["dotnet"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/imwkxe","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/imwkxe/unions_merged_into_dotnet_11_preview_3"}]